00:03:28.623 --> 00:03:30.304
So we used to have a scalability problem.

00:03:31.925 --> 00:03:33.586
Now we don't really have a scalability

00:03:33.626 --> 00:03:34.306
problem anymore,

00:03:34.325 --> 00:03:37.847
but it kind of this led to a

00:03:37.887 --> 00:03:38.427
new problem,

00:03:38.568 --> 00:03:40.609
namely that Ethereum and these various

00:03:40.669 --> 00:03:41.028
rollups,

00:03:41.449 --> 00:03:43.629
they don't talk with each other in the

00:03:43.669 --> 00:03:47.692
same way that things on Ethereum can talk

00:03:47.711 --> 00:03:48.651
to each other natively.

00:03:49.304 --> 00:03:49.563
Okay,

00:03:49.883 --> 00:03:53.844
so the Ethereum economic zone is a way

00:03:54.384 --> 00:03:55.465
