do you see this card ethereum in many

00:04:31.321 --> 00:04:33.401
ways it looks exactly like the ethereum we

00:04:33.442 --> 00:04:36.644
had before we got edges right so um

00:04:36.843 --> 00:04:41.045
the beauty of ethereum um beforehand was

00:04:41.305 --> 00:04:42.307
that um

00:04:43.499 --> 00:04:45.899
